M|references|// Push event
M|references|dataLayer.push({
M|references|'event': 'event_name',
M|references|'property1': 'value1',
M|references|'property2': 'value2'
M|references|});
M|references|```
M|references|```javascript
M|references|// Set on page load (before GTM container)
M|references|window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
M|references|dataLayer.push({
M|references|'pageType': 'product',
M|references|'contentGroup': 'products',
M|references|'user': {
M|references|'loggedIn': true,
M|references|'userId': '12345',
M|references|'userType': 'premium'
M|references|}
M|references|});
M|references|```
M|references|```javascript
