M|references|**Tag Type:** Google anl: GA4 cfg
M|references|**Settings:**
M|references|- Measurement ID: G-XXXXXXXX
M|references|- Send page view: Checked (for pageviews)
M|references|- User Properties: Add any user-level dimensions
M|references|**Trigger:** All Pages
M|references|**Tag Type:** Google anl: GA4 Event
M|references|**Settings:**
M|references|- cfg Tag: Select your config tag
M|references|- Event Name: {{DL - event_name}} or hardcode
M|references|- Event Parameters: Add parameters from dataLayer
M|references|**Trigger:** Custom Event with event name match
M|references|**Tag Type:** Custom HTML
M|references|```html
M|references|<script>
M|references|!function(f,b,e,v,n,t,s)
M|references|{if(f.fbq)return;n=f.fbq=function(){n.callMethod?
M|references|n.callMethod.apply(n,arguments):n.queue.push(arguments)};
M|references|if(!f._fbq)f._fbq=n;n.push=n;n.loaded=!0;n.version='2.0';
M|references|n.queue=[];t=b.createElement(e);t.async=!0;
M|references|t.src=v;s=b.getElementsByTagName(e)[0];
M|references|s.parentNode.insertBefore(t,s)}(window, doc,'script',
M|references|'https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/fbevents.js');
M|references|fbq('init', 'YOUR_PIXEL_ID');
M|references|fbq('track', 'PageView');
M|references|</script>
M|references|```
M|references|**Trigger:** All Pages
M|references|**Tag Type:** Custom HTML
